snippet.title: Supermarket VR - The Game
snippet.description:
New Virtual Reality game : Supermarket VR.

Oculus Rift: https://www.oculus.com/experiences/rift/1408091119267920

Buy products in supermarkets moving with your shopping cart and grabbing items with your hands. Teleport to sections easily.
Complete shopping list in time/money limits and avoid collision with other people. 
Complete a lot of missions !

Play to mini-games in a supermarket interior: basketball, bottle flip challenge, bowling, throwing ball and handball.

The furture of online buying has arrived and can be funny !
The future is here!
